            <div type="l">
                <column>1</column>
                <head>Letter from Judge Douglas</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary>The Vindicator makes fun of Judge Douglas for trying to dictate the
                    platform of the Democratic party.</commentary>
                <transcript>
                    <p/>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names>
                    <name>
                        <ln>Douglas</ln>
                        <fn/>
                        <sf/>
                        <pf>Judge</pf>
                    </name>
                    <name>
                        <ln>Durr</ln>
                        <fn>J.B.</fn>
                        <sf/>
                        <pf/>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>Letter from Judge Douglas says he will refuse the Democratic nomination for
                    President if the party repudiates such time-honored party principles as refusing
                    to support the re-opening of the slave trade.</summary>
            </div>
